<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٨٢ - وَمِنْهَا قولهمك <span style="color:#950000">" الْحَيَاءُ يَمْنَعُ الرِّزْقَ "</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٨٣ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" حُبُّ الْهِرَّةِ مِنَ الإِيمَانِ "</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٨٤ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" قُلُوبُ الشُّعَرَاءِ خَزَائِنُ الرَّحْمَنِ "</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٨٥ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" خَيْرُ خَلِّكُمْ خَلُّ خَمْرِكُمْ "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>٨٦ - وَمِنْهَا الْأَحَادِيث الَّتِي تروى فِي <span style="color:#950000">" أَكْلِ سَلَطَةِ الْحَشِيشِ "</span> لم يثبت مِنْهَا شَيْء.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٧٨ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْهَا قَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span style="color:#950000">" لَوْلا أَنَّ السُّؤَّالَ يَكْذِبُونَ مَا قُدِّسَ مَنْ رَدَّهُمْ "</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>